arStrings.szText: The Tree of Whispers told us to "seek a coffin beyond the wrecks." Lorath and Neyrelle have gone  towards the eastern shore in search. I should join them.
We've found the coffin the Tree of Whispers spoke of, sitting among a massive collection of shipwrecks. Whatever Elias is hiding, somehow it's out there.
Removing Elias' finger from the altar caused the temple to sink further into the murky waters. I was able to escape, but only barely. I should return to Lorath as quickly as possible.
The ancient coffin has brought me to some kind of ancient, sunken temple. Elias' secret hides in these forgotten depths somewhere.
